    dc:description "FIGURE 18. Syntype sheets of Artemisia tangutica var. tomentosa. B. Inset a: portion of a leaf, adaxially viscid-pubescent; inset b: capitula, phyllaries abaxially sparsely pubescent." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6501394/files/figure.png" ;
