<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6501396>
    dc:description "FIGURE 19. Holotype (A), isotype (B), and non-type (C, D) sheets of Artemisia robusta (= A. strongylocephala var. sinensis f. robusta), all from Gongshan County in Yunnan.A, B. G. Forrest 13379 (E, PE). C. T.T. Yu 20286 (PE). D. T.T. Yu 20724 (PE)." ;
